revolutionary type of scuba suit

38:27.600 --> 38:31.440
that will allow humans
to breathe liquid air.

38:31.560 --> 38:34.190
Key to his invention
is a special solution

38:34.310 --> 38:36.780
of highly oxygenated
perfluorocarbons,

38:36.900 --> 38:38.530
a type of liquid

38:38.650 --> 38:41.860
that can dissolve
enormous quantities of gas.

38:41.990 --> 38:45.780
And while the technology
is still in development,

38:45.910 --> 38:49.370
if LandÃ© succeeds,
humans will be able to dive

38:49.500 --> 38:52.420
to more extreme depths
than ever before.

38:52.540 --> 38:56.250
In these dark recesses
of Earth's oceans,

38:56.380 --> 38:58.960
could we discover that humans
share the Earth

38:59.090 --> 39:02.510
with much more intelligent
and sophisticated life-forms

39:02.630 --> 39:05.260
than anything found on land?

39:05.390 --> 39:09.520
Frankly, we have no idea
what might be down there.

39:09.640 --> 39:12.140
Exploration has been
very limited.

39:12.270 --> 39:14.690
There are vast parts
of the ocean

39:14.810 --> 39:18.020
about which we know
absolutely nothing.

39:18.150 --> 39:20.940
As humans, we tend to believe
that we have dominion

39:21.070 --> 39:25.120
over the Earth, but in the vast
oceans beneath us,

39:25.240 --> 39:28.740
there could be all kinds
of advanced civilizations.

39:28.870 --> 39:32.040
Even ones that have been here
for much longer

39:32.160 --> 39:34.120
than we've been on this planet.

39:34.250 --> 39:37.340
And they've come here
from other solar systems

39:37.460 --> 39:39.710
and then came to our planet

39:39.840 --> 39:42.880
where they're now
living underwater.

39:43.010 --> 39:44.970
And it seems incredible to us,

39:45.090 --> 39:47.640
but we may be seeing
their ships,

39:47.760 --> 39:50.770
these USOs coming
out of the water,

39:50.890 --> 39:54.850
and there may be some
highly advanced civilization

39:54.980 --> 39:59.070
that's in these vast oceans
that we have yet to explore.

39:59.190 --> 40:01.110
Anything could be down there.

40:01.230 --> 40:04.450
TSOUKALOS:
Some people have proposed

40:04.570 --> 40:09.200
that the Earth served
as some gigantic Petri dish.

40:09.330 --> 40:12.750
And so you have to wonder
what else can emerge on Earth

40:12.870 --> 40:14.500
that we don't even know about?

40:16.460 --> 40:18.210
HENRY: Could there be more
sophisticated life-forms

40:18.340 --> 40:20.380
than us,
not just on distant planets,

40:20.500 --> 40:23.050
but right here
in our own oceans?

40:23.170 --> 40:26.180
Not aliens, but earthlings?

40:26.300 --> 40:29.430
NARRATOR: If extraterrestrials
seeded the Earth

40:29.550 --> 40:31.850
and continue to use it
as a genetic laboratory,

40:31.970 --> 40:34.390
as ancient astronaut
theorists suggest,

40:34.520 --> 40:36.980
could further
deep-sea exploration

40:37.100 --> 40:40.690
discover a species
more advanced than humans?

40:40.820 --> 40:43.990
Perhaps creatures resembling
the amphibious gods

40:44.110 --> 40:46.740
depicted by our ancestors?

40:46.860 --> 40:49.660
And will we only have true
dominion over the Earth

40:49.780 --> 40:52.330
once we are able
to fully explore

40:52.450 --> 40:55.710
and inhabit
these depths as well?

40:55.830 --> 40:58.210
Some ancient astronaut
theorists believe

40:58.330 --> 41:02.590
the creatures of the deep may
already have plans for humanity.

41:02.710 --> 41:05.010
Are there extraterrestrials
in fact in our oceans

41:05.130 --> 41:08.890
that are experimenting
with different types of beings?

41:09.010 --> 41:12.180
And are they looking ultimately
to upgrade humanity

41:12.310 --> 41:14.180
with some of these discoveries?

41:14.310 --> 41:16.180
Is that what's in our future,

41:16.310 --> 41:18.480
that there could be
extraterrestrial beings

41:18.600 --> 41:20.360
that will come out
of Earth's ocean

41:20.480 --> 41:22.900
that will deliver some kind
of revelation that says,

41:23.020 --> 41:25.400
"Hey guys,
this isn't all there is.

41:25.530 --> 41:29.950
You can, in fact, transform
yourself into this,"

41:30.070 --> 41:32.620
and that will be the future
evolution of humanity.

41:32.740 --> 41:35.500
NARRATOR: Instead of looking
for alien civilizations

41:35.620 --> 41:37.790
beyond our solar system,

41:37.910 --> 41:41.710
might we find them in the
darkest depths of our oceans?

41:44.050 --> 41:46.010
Is it possible
that there is already a species

41:46.130 --> 41:48.050
more advanced than humans

41:48.170 --> 41:51.340
hiding out in places
we can't reach

41:51.470 --> 41:55.810
that have been there
for thousands of years?

41:55.930 --> 41:58.730
Perhaps we will make
alien contact

41:58.850 --> 42:01.690
not when they come down
from the sky

42:01.810 --> 42:04.520
but when they reemerge
from the sea.
